Output demo/diag.gif
Set Shell zsh
Set FontSize 13
Set Width 1000
Set Height 620
Hide
Type "setopt interactive_comments" Enter
Type "source ~/Developer/busbarAI/busbarAI/demo/env.sh" Enter
Type "export CLAUDE_CONFIG_DIR=/tmp/clean-claude" Enter
Type "cd /tmp/agentdemo && clear" Enter
Show
Type "claude" Enter
Sleep 6s
Screenshot demo/s1.png
Type "say only the word: ready"
Sleep 500ms
Enter
Sleep 12s
Screenshot demo/s2.png
Ctrl+C Sleep 300ms Ctrl+C
